					<div class="relative rounded-lg shadow-lg bg-[#222] border border-[#222] bg-opacity-50 px-8 py-4 w-96">
						<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-35 bg-[url(https://ophxthemushroom.pages.dev/react.svg)] bg-no-repeat bg-right-top bg-contain blur"></div>
						<div class="relative z-10 space-y-4">
							<p class="text-left text-3xl font-medium text-white">Web Development</p>
							<p class="text-left text-gray-300">I have been messing with web development ever since I was 9 years old. I first started with just HTML and CSS but then moved onto frameworks like React, Svelte, ect.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="relative rounded-lg shadow-lg bg-[#222] border border-[#222] bg-opacity-50 px-8 py-4 w-96">
						<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-35 bg-[url(https://ophxthemushroom.pages.dev/discord.svg)] bg-no-repeat bg-right-top bg-contain blur"></div>
						<div class="relative z-10 space-y-4">
