						<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-35 bg-[url(https://ophxthemushroom.pages.dev/cpp.svg)] bg-no-repeat bg-right-top bg-contain blur"></div>
						<div class="relative z-10 space-y-4">
							<p class="text-left text-white text-3xl font-medium">Cheat Development</p>
							<p class="text-left text-gray-300">I used to mess around with making cheats for online games. But, a few months ago I completely quit. It's a real pain in the ass lmao.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="relative rounded-lg shadow-lg bg-[#222] border border-[#222] bg-opacity-50 px-8 py-4 w-96">
						<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-35 bg-[url(https://ophxthemushroom.pages.dev/shroom.svg)] bg-no-repeat bg-right-top bg-contain blur"></div>
						<div class="relative z-10 space-y-4">
							<p class="text-left text-white text-3xl font-medium">Growing Shrooms</p>
